      "earl:test": {
        "@id": "https://hologram.os/conformance/os2#holo-mind-soul",
        "dcterms:title": "Holo Mind PHASE 3 (ADR-0081) — the SOUL, one objective made operational. (1) INTRINSIC DRIVES (anima's digital_desire, os/usr/lib/holo/holo-mind-soul.mjs): homeostatic urges (epistemic hunger Hₑ, fitness Fₐ) that PROPOSE curiosity/self goals — a proposal is NEVER an act; it raises a holo:Intent that runs the ordinary loop where the fail-closed conscience (ADR-033) gates every step, so self-discipline is STRUCTURAL (no path from a drive to an effect can skip the gate). The drive state is integer-only (no clock/random) so a tick re-derives (Law L5, the holo-heal idiom). (2) The COHERENCE measure — the soul's utility (maximize SIGNAL over NOISE): DETERMINISTIC and re-derivable ON PURPOSE (signal = a re-derivable + novel effect; noise = the unverifiable or duplicate), so the objective CANNOT be Goodharted by a model self-grade; the five JUDGED output-court principles (Care · Fairness · Autonomy · Responsibility · Justice, ADR-033 judgeOutput) are the model-judged measure of a GOOD action, wired at the loop's VERIFY (stochastic — honest boundary). (3) Self-verifying USER + SELF models: a deepening PRIVATE-FIRST user model (adapts to + teaches the user) and a persistent self identity with a divergence score (anima's SelfModel); κ-objects, revisioned (prov:wasRevisionOf), DURABLE (the OS κ-store), NEVER published (Law L1 + Data Sovereignty / Holo Privacy). Witnessed tools/holo-mind-soul-witness.mjs (8/8, incl. the REAL output court blocking PII on the Dignity red line); wired live into holo-mind-ui.js (window.HoloMind.drives / proposeGoals / runProposals / updateUser / snapshotSelf / primeDirective); required + in gate.mjs LIVE."
      },
