      "earl:test": {
        "@id": "https://hologram.os/conformance/os2#holo-mind-orchestrate",
        "dcterms:title": "Holo Mind PHASE 4 (ADR-0081) — orchestration at scale. PARALLEL SUB-AGENTS: a sub-agent is an ordinary conscience-gated Holo Mind loop run; orchestrate (os/usr/lib/holo/holo-mind-orchestrate.mjs + the binding) runs N CONCURRENTLY (Promise.all over runLoop — content-addressed seals can't collide; the corpus head is touched ONCE, after the barrier, no race) and composes ONE self-verifying PROV-O WORK RECEIPT over their receipts — the Holo Orchestrate idiom (ADR-0045): the root κ is proof of the WHOLE collaboration, verifyDeep re-runs every sub-receipt with no orchestrator to trust, and a TAMPERED sub-receipt breaks the root (Law L5). Each sub-agent's every step still passes the fail-closed conscience (ADR-033) — orchestration adds reach, never a gate bypass; scoped sub-authority rides the existing UCAN seam (ADR-0042). SCHEDULED TASKS: a holo:ScheduledTask is a re-derivable κ-object {utterance, everyMs}; an OPT-IN in-tab ticker (window.HoloMind.startScheduler) fires DUE tasks through the gated loop, the CLOCK read at the EDGE (Date.now in the ticker; dueTasks is PURE) so the core stays re-derivation-safe — honest scope: serverless + in-tab, tasks fire only while the tab is open (no background server, like cron / Claude Desktop). UCAN-SCOPED SUB-AGENT DELEGATION (ADR-0042, re-expressed substrate-native): each sub-agent acts under a holo:Delegation — a NARROWED, revocable capability (a scoped verb set ⊆ its granter's; the attenuation chain is content-addressed via prov:wasDerivedFrom, so ESCALATION is caught by re-derivation); orchestrate ATTENUATES each sub-agent's roster to its grant, and REVOKING a delegation (window.HoloMind.revoke) invalidates its whole SUBTREE → that sub-agent is refused; the work receipt commits to the delegation κ each sub acted under (who acted, under what authority — ADR-0045 ⊕ 0042). Honest scope: the full UCAN signature / principal-alignment proof engine is the agent stack's (own.verifyChain / verify_delegation, ADR-0049). Witnessed tools/holo-mind-orchestrate-witness.mjs (8/8: work composes + re-derives, a tamper breaks the root, the task re-derives, due-logic is pure, delegation attenuates + scopes the roster + revokes the subtree); wired live (window.HoloMind.orchestrate / schedule / startScheduler / delegate / revoke); required + in gate.mjs LIVE."
      },
