        "dcterms:title": "Holo Hub commerce kernel (ADR-0094) — Medusa's commerce MATH runs in-tab, VERBATIM, as a deterministic Forge κ-transform (not re-implemented). holo-hub-kernel.mjs compiles Medusa's vendored tax+totals math (totals/math.ts MathBN, big-number.ts, tax/index.ts + pure common helpers + pinned bignumber.js@9.1.2) through the in-tree esbuild κ-transform (κ(source)⊕esbuild⊕flags → κ(kernel)) into one self-contained ESM kernel; 0-network at runtime. Witnessed tools/holo-hub-kernel-witness.mjs (bundles self-contained · deterministic rebuild → identical κ, L5 · 7/7 source files re-hash to their pinned κ, verbatim · loads + runs: calculateTaxTotal 200@10%=20, multi-rate 400@(8.25+1.75)%=40, tax-inclusive/exclusive round-trips, BigNumber 0.1+0.2===0.3 · 0-network)."
